# SONNTAG AG Website - UI Blocks Integration Rules

## 🎯 **UI Blocks Integration Overview**
Specific rules for adapting downloaded Tailwind CSS Plus components to SONNTAG AG's clean white/black theme while preserving original design quality.

## 📥 **Downloaded Component Handling**

### **Component Source Tracking**
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Always include source information
/**
 * Component: Simple Centered Hero
 * Source: Tailwind CSS Plus - Marketing/Hero Sections
 * Original ID: simple-centered
 * Adaptation: Colors only (white/black theme)
 * Structure: Preserved exactly as downloaded
 */

// ❌ BAD - Missing source information
/**
 * Hero component
 * Custom design
 */
```

### **File Organization for Downloaded Components**
```
src/components/ui-blocks/
├── blocks/                    # Downloaded components
│   ├── marketing/            # Marketing components
│   │   ├── hero-sections/    # Hero section variants
│   │   ├── feature-sections/ # Feature showcases
│   │   ├── cta-sections/     # Call-to-action
│   │   └── pricing-sections/ # Pricing displays
│   ├── about/                # About page components
│   └── team/                 # Team showcase components
├── adapted/                   # SONNTAG AG adapted versions
│   ├── hero/                 # Adapted hero sections
│   ├── services/             # Adapted service components
│   └── about/                # Adapted about components
└── manifest.json             # Component index
```

## 🎨 **Component Adaptation Process**

### **Step 1: Preserve Original**
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Keep original structure intact
// Original downloaded component
<div className="bg-indigo-600 text-white">
  <h1 className="text-4xl font-bold">Original Title</h1>
</div>

// ❌ BAD - Don't change structure
<div className="bg-white text-black">
  <h2 className="text-3xl font-semibold">Modified Title</h2>  // Changed tag and styling
</div>
```

### **Step 2: Color Adaptation Only**
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Systematic color replacement
// Original: bg-indigo-600 text-white
// Adapted: bg-white text-black border-gray-200

// Color mapping rules:
const COLOR_MAPPING = {
  // Backgrounds
  'bg-indigo-600': 'bg-white',
  'bg-gray-900': 'bg-white',
  'bg-blue-600': 'bg-white',
  
  // Text
  'text-white': 'text-black',
  'text-indigo-600': 'text-gray-700',
  'text-blue-600': 'text-gray-700',
  
  // Borders
  'border-indigo-600': 'border-gray-200',
  'border-blue-600': 'border-gray-200',
  
  // Hover states
  'hover:bg-indigo-700': 'hover:bg-gray-50',
  'hover:bg-blue-700': 'hover:bg-gray-50',
}
```

### **Step 3: Maintain Interactions**
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Preserve all interactive states
className="bg-white text-black border-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-gray-500 focus:border-gray-500 transition-colors duration-200"

// ❌ BAD - Removing interactive states
className="bg-white text-black border-gray-200"  // Missing hover, focus, transitions
```

## 🔧 **Technical Adaptation Rules**

### **Tailwind Class Preservation**
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Keep all utility classes
className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32"

// ❌ BAD - Removing utility classes
className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-24"  // Missing responsive variants
```

### **Component Props Interface**
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Maintain original props structure
interface HeroSectionProps {
  title: string
  subtitle?: string
  ctaText: string
  onCtaClick: () => void
  // Add SONNTAG AG specific props
  isPrimary?: boolean
  brandAccent?: 'blue' | 'gold'
}

// ❌ BAD - Completely changing props
interface HeroProps {  // Different name
  heading: string      // Different prop names
  subheading?: string
  buttonText: string
  onClick: () => void
}
```

### **Import Structure**
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD - Clear import hierarchy
// 1. React and Next.js
import { useState } from 'react'
import { useRouter } from 'next/navigation'

// 2. Downloaded component (preserved)
import { SimpleCenteredHero } from '@/components/ui-blocks/blocks/marketing/hero-sections/simple-centered'

// 3. SONNTAG AG adaptations
import { SonntagHeroSection } from '@/components/ui-blocks/adapted/hero/sonntag-hero'

// 4. Shared utilities
import { formatDate } from '@/lib/utils'

// ❌ BAD - Mixed import sources
import { Hero } from '@/components/hero'  // Unclear source
import { Button } from '@/ui/button'      // Inconsistent paths
```

## 📋 **Component Adaptation Checklist**

### **Before Adaptation**
- [ ] Component downloaded and saved to `blocks/` directory
- [ ] Original structure documented
- [ ] Color scheme analyzed
- [ ] Interactive states identified
- [ ] Responsive behavior noted

### **During Adaptation**
- [ ] Create new file in `adapted/` directory
- [ ] Copy original structure exactly
- [ ] Apply color mapping systematically
- [ ] Preserve all Tailwind utilities
- [ ] Maintain responsive breakpoints
- [ ] Keep all interactive states

### **After Adaptation**
- [ ] Test responsive behavior
- [ ] Verify color contrast ratios
- [ ] Check accessibility compliance
- [ ] Update manifest.json
- [ ] Document adaptation changes
- [ ] Test with SONNTAG AG content

## 🎯 **Specific Component Adaptation Examples**

### **Hero Section Adaptation**
```typescript
// Original (downloaded)
export function SimpleCenteredHero() {
  return (
    <div className="bg-indigo-600">
      <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32">
        <div className="text-center">
          <h1 className="text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-6xl">
            Deploy faster
          </h1>
          <p className="mt-6 text-lg text-indigo-100">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
          </p>
          <button className="mt-8 bg-white text-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-50">
            Get started
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  )
}

// Adapted for SONNTAG AG
export function SonntagHeroSection() {
  return (
    <div className="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
      <div className="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 sm:py-32">
        <div className="text-center">
          <h1 className="text-4xl font-bold text-black sm:text-6xl">
            Wir sichern Lebenswerke
          </h1>
          <p className="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600">
            Führende M&A Beratung in Gießen
          </p>
          <button className="mt-8 bg-black text-white hover:bg-gray-800">
            Mehr erfahren
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  )
}
```

